dcterms:description: A publicly available dataset consisting of health records of 46,520 intensive care unit (ICU) patients over 11 years. The dataset includes demographics, laboratory test results, microbiology test results, diagnoses, medications, procedures, medical notes, and more. It is used for diagnosis prediction tasks and includes structured and semi-structured data.
